src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fax0Sere.png&h=5de37ae9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我用email呼籲公務員罷工<br />\n內容係copy以下post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1376339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1376339/page/1</a>"}]}